      "text": "{user}さん、どこに行ったんだろ？\n用事があるって出て行ってから帰って来ないけど……",
      "startTime": 4.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7810,
          "startTime": 8.61
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.9333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ごま鯖ンナちゃん！？\n今日は来てくれてありがとう～！",
      "startTime": 12.4734962397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さくら……ちゃん！\nこちらこそ今日はよろしくお願いしますサバ！",
      "startTime": 18.1666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.3333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（着ぐるみなんて初めて着たけど）\n（まさかこんなに暑くて前が見辛いとは……）",
      "startTime": 24.8000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　鯖ンナちゃん、ちょっと声が変だけど\nどうしたの？",
      "startTime": 34.1333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　えっと……ちょっと夏風邪をひいてしまった\nサバ！　でも、心配はいらないサバよ～",
      "startTime": 39.5674535371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "なら良かったよ。ごま鯖ンナちゃんのファンの\nみんなにも喜んでもらえる楽しいライブにしようね！",
      "startTime": 46.8666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.9666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、危ない危ない……俺だとバレないように）\n（最後までやり切らなければ……）",
      "startTime": 53.7379217164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば、ごま鯖ンナちゃん\n{user}さんを見なかった？",
      "startTime": 59.5000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.0000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　えっと……か、彼ならスタッフさんとの急な\n打ち合わせが入ったって言ってたサバ！",
      "startTime": 67.2333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブはちゃんと観るから頑張ってと\n伝言を預かっているサバよ！",
      "startTime": 72.5463332347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.0666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9478836618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ！　今日も忙しそうだなぁ。あれ？\nでも、いつの間にそんなに仲良くなったの？",
      "startTime": 81.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さっき一緒にご飯を食べたんだサバ！\n同じごま鯖を食べたら、もう心の同志サバよ！",
      "startTime": 87.9666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.0000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだ！　ふふ、ごま鯖ンナちゃんが\nみんなと仲良くなってくれて嬉しいな～",
      "startTime": 97.2333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　ステージでやるアレ、やって欲しいな！\nリハーサルも兼ねて！",
      "startTime": 105.0000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、アレ？　アレって何だ！？）\n（分からない……が、ええい、もうやけくそだ！）",
      "startTime": 109.7000006358,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6070.284527300004,
          "startTime": 115.7702851631
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごま鯖式ムーンウォークサバー！\nよっ、ほっ、ポゥ！",
      "startTime": 118.3000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.2333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "あはは！　本物のごま鯖式ムーン魚ークだ！\nやけに軽快なのがごま鯖ンナちゃんの魅力だよね！",
      "startTime": 125.1333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（思い付きでムーンウォークをしてみたが）\n（まさか合っていたとは……）",
      "startTime": 132.2000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.2666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "本番前に変なお願いしちゃってごめんね！\n笑ったら喉渇いちゃった。えっと、お水は……",
      "startTime": 137.6333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それならさっき怜が最後の一本を持ち出していたぞ\nそろそろ補充分の水をスタッフさんが持って来るはずだ",
      "startTime": 147.8000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.4333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　や、やけに詳しいねごま鯖ンナちゃん\nそれに、その喋り方……",
      "startTime": 157.3421169281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.8000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "――って、伝えておくようにさっきマネージャーに\n言われたのを思い出したサバ！",
      "startTime": 163.1000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.2000006375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうなんだ。こういう心配をするだろうって\n{user}さんに見抜かれてたのかな",
      "startTime": 170.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ごま鯖ンナちゃん",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（こ、この調子で本当に乗り切れるだろうか）\n（絶対にボロを出さないようにしなくては……）",
      "startTime": 176.5000006358,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 180.8333339691
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.5833339691
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.5833339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "福岡のみなさーん、こんにちはー！\n今日はライブに来てくれてありがとう～！",
      "startTime": 185.6333339691,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12272.562083600007,
          "startTime": 197.9058960527
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.9666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.9000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_12_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "今日はなんと！　素敵な特別ゲストを招待してます！\nというわけで、どうぞ――ごま鯖ンナちゃん！",
      "startTime": 193.9000006358,
      "sfxList": []
